      "text": "provider          HumanFeedbackProvider      No        Custom provider for async/non-blocking\n                                                                                        feedback. See Async Human Feedback\n\n  learn             bool                                          No         Enable HITL learning: distill lessons from feedback \n                                                                                        and pre-review future output. Default False. \n                                                                                        See Learning from Feedback\n\n learn_limit        int                                          No           Max past lessons to recall for pre-review. Default 5",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "provider          HumanFeedbackProvider      No        Custom provider for async/non-blocking\n                                                                                        feedback. See Async Human Feedback\n\n  learn             bool                                          No         Enable HITL learning: distill lessons from feedback \n                                                                                        and pre-review future output. Default False. \n                                                                                        See Learning from Feedback\n\n learn_limit        int                                          No           Max past lessons to recall for pre-review. Default 5",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
