      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "human_feedback\n\nAsync Human Feedback (Non-Blocking)\n\nBy default, @human_feedback blocks execution waiting for console input. \nFor production applications, you may need async/non-blocking feedback that integrates \nwith external systems like Slack, email, webhooks, or APIs.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "human_feedback\n\nAsync Human Feedback (Non-Blocking)\n\nBy default, @human_feedback blocks execution waiting for console input. \nFor production applications, you may need async/non-blocking feedback that integrates \nwith external systems like Slack, email, webhooks, or APIs.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
