      "updated": 1774096739221,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Handling Paused Flows\n\nWhen using an async provider, kickoff() returns a HumanFeedbackPending \nobject instead of raising an exception:\n\nCode\nflow = ReviewFlow()\nresult = flow.kickoff()\n\nif isinstance(result, HumanFeedbackPending):\n    # Flow is paused, state is automatically persisted\n    print(f\"Waiting for feedback at: {result.callback_info['webhook_url']}\")\n    print(f\"Flow ID: {result.context.flow_id}\")\nelse:\n    # Normal completion\n    print(f\"Flow completed: {result}\")",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Handling Paused Flows\n\nWhen using an async provider, kickoff() returns a HumanFeedbackPending \nobject instead of raising an exception:\n\nCode\nflow = ReviewFlow()\nresult = flow.kickoff()\n\nif isinstance(result, HumanFeedbackPending):\n    # Flow is paused, state is automatically persisted\n    print(f\"Waiting for feedback at: {result.callback_info['webhook_url']}\")\n    print(f\"Flow ID: {result.context.flow_id}\")\nelse:\n    # Normal completion\n    print(f\"Flow completed: {result}\")",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "Twkh1KbgZ1zNgOJkSRyWf",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 248.3333282470703,
      "y": 1532.499930991069,
      "width": 579.0993041992188,
      "height": 432,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a5",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 223391416,
      "version": 10,
      "versionNonce": 661423560,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774096737422,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\nResuming a Paused Flow\n\nWhen feedback arrives (e.g., via webhook), resume the flow:\nCode\n# Sync handler:\ndef handle_feedback_webhook(flow_id: str, feedback: str):\n    flow = ReviewFlow.from_pending(flow_id)\n    result = flow.resume(feedback)\n    return result\n\n# Async handler (FastAPI, aiohttp, etc.):\nasync def handle_feedback_webhook(flow_id: str, feedback: str):\n    flow = ReviewFlow.from_pending(flow_id)\n    result = await flow.resume_async(feedback)\n    return result",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\nResuming a Paused Flow\n\nWhen feedback arrives (e.g., via webhook), resume the flow:\nCode\n# Sync handler:\ndef handle_feedback_webhook(flow_id: str, feedback: str):\n    flow = ReviewFlow.from_pending(flow_id)\n    result = flow.resume(feedback)\n    return result\n\n# Async handler (FastAPI, aiohttp, etc.):\nasync def handle_feedback_webhook(flow_id: str, feedback: str):\n    flow = ReviewFlow.from_pending(flow_id)\n    result = await flow.resume_async(feedback)\n    return result",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
