      "text": "✅ flow_id stays SAME throughout entire session\n✅ WebhookProvider = just pause + save + metadata\n✅ feedback travels via path parameter\n✅ from_pending() restores correct flow\n✅ resume_async() continues from exact pause point\n✅ LLM mapped \"approved\" → on_approved() fired\n✅ Flow ended cleanly",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "✅ flow_id stays SAME throughout entire session\n✅ WebhookProvider = just pause + save + metadata\n✅ feedback travels via path parameter\n✅ from_pending() restores correct flow\n✅ resume_async() continues from exact pause point\n✅ LLM mapped \"approved\" → on_approved() fired\n✅ Flow ended cleanly",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
