      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1774284578962,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "flow.kickoff(inputs={\"topic\": \"What is Generative AI\"})\n        ↓\nget_topic()          ✅\n        ↓\ngenerate_draft()     ✅  draft created\n        ↓\nreview_draft()       ✅  HITL paused, showed to human\n        ↓\nhuman gave feedback  ✅  revision 1\n        ↓\n@router → \"retry\"    ✅\n        ↓\n@start(\"retry\") → generate_draft() 🔁  revision 2\n        ↓\nreview_draft()       ✅  HITL paused again\n        ↓\nhuman gave feedback  ✅  revision 2\n        ↓\n@router → \"retry\"    ✅\n        ↓\n@start(\"retry\") → generate_draft() 🔁  revision 3\n        ↓\nrevision_count >= MAX_ITERATIONS\n        ↓\n@router → \"max_retry_exceeded\" ✅\n        ↓\n⚠ Max revisions reached. Saving last version. ✅",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "flow.kickoff(inputs={\"topic\": \"What is Generative AI\"})\n        ↓\nget_topic()          ✅\n        ↓\ngenerate_draft()     ✅  draft created\n        ↓\nreview_draft()       ✅  HITL paused, showed to human\n        ↓\nhuman gave feedback  ✅  revision 1\n        ↓\n@router → \"retry\"    ✅\n        ↓\n@start(\"retry\") → generate_draft() 🔁  revision 2\n        ↓\nreview_draft()       ✅  HITL paused again\n        ↓\nhuman gave feedback  ✅  revision 2\n        ↓\n@router → \"retry\"    ✅\n        ↓\n@start(\"retry\") → generate_draft() 🔁  revision 3\n        ↓\nrevision_count >= MAX_ITERATIONS\n        ↓\n@router → \"max_retry_exceeded\" ✅\n        ↓\n⚠ Max revisions reached. Saving last version. ✅",
